  "original_title": "\u2019\u2019\u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dad\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dad\u0dca \u0db1\u0dd1\u2019\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"No letter of resignation yet\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena said that he has not yet received President Gotabaya Rajapaksa's letter of resignation.",
        "Sources say that this situation has arisen as the President has not yet reached the destination."
